      <title>意大利银行业并购活动加剧，Ifis 竞购 illimity</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/ifis-bids-illimity-italys-banking-ma-intensifies-2025-01-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利伊菲斯银行（Banca Ifis）周三表示，将以 2.98 亿欧元（3.09 亿美元）的现金和股票收购竞争对手 illimity 专业贷款机构，以在日益严峻的市场中增强实力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/ifis-bids-illimity-italys-banking-ma-intensifies-2025-01-08/</guid>
